OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FWords by ITV News' Jess Omari and
OL,8,FJames Mates from Lebanon
OL,10,FThe scene has become all too familiar,
OL,11,Fmassive Israeli airstrikes against the
OL,12,Fancient port city of Tyre.
OL,14,FThe city, from which the Phoenicians
OL,15,Fonce sailed to found the Carthaginian
OL,16,FEmpire, is a UNESCO World Heritage
OL,17,FSite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
