FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780707788
OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FCultural treasures from the great
OL,8,Fempires of the Romans, the Mamluks and
OL,9,Fthe Ottomans are everywhere here ` a
OL,10,Ffew miles outside Tyre, three of the
OL,11,Ffour golden domes of the Chamaa
OL,12,FCitadel, believed by some to be the
OL,13,Fresting place of St Peter, now in
OL,14,Fruins.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
