CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780707788
OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FLebanon lies in the cradle of
OL,8,Fcivilisation; In April, UNESCO granted
OL,9,Fenhanced protection to 39 cultural
OL,10,Fheritage sites here.
OL,12,FAn emergency measure meant to shield
OL,13,Fthese historical, religious, and
OL,14,Farchaeological properties from attack
OL,15,For being used for military purposes.
OL,17,FThis special classification grants
OL,18,Fthese assets the highest level of
OL,19,Flegal immunity under the 1954 Hague
OL,20,FConvention. Making their targeting
OL,21,Fillegal under international law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
