CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780707788
OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FSo far, it's had a limited effect.
OL,9,FWe visited the city of Baalbek and its
OL,10,Fmagnificent Roman temples of Bacchus
OL,11,Fand Jupiter.
OL,13,FBut this is Hezbollah territory, and
OL,14,Fthe war is raging here.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780707788
OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FThe governor of Baalbek, Bachir Khodr,
OL,8,Fshowed us around the temple complex
OL,9,Fbegun by the Phoenicians and completed
OL,10,Fby the Romans 2000 years ago, the six
OL,11,Fcolumns of the Temple of Jupiter still
OL,12,Fstanding in tribute to Rome's
OL,13,Farchitectural genius.
OL,15,FTwice in the last two years,
OL,16,Fairstrikes have come within a few
OL,17,Fhundred metres of this jewel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780707788
OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FThe first airstrike from the early
OL,8,Fstages of this war two years ago
OL,9,Freduced an Ottoman building of
OL,10,Fhistorical importance to rubble. The
OL,11,FRoman ruins narrowly escaped.
OL,13,FTo launch an airstrike near here is to
OL,14,Flaunch an airstrike near the Acropolis
OL,15,Fin Athens or the Colosseum in Rome.
OL,17,FKhodr told us this heritage site
OL,18,Fdoesn't only belong to Lebanon, but to
OL,19,Fhumanity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780707788
OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FThe Israeli Army, though, say they are
OL,8,Ftargeting Hezbollah military
OL,9,Finfrastructure. Khodr is at pains to
OL,10,Fprove that accusation false in Baalbek.
OL,12,F"We were really worried about this
OL,13,Fhistorical heritage, we have repeated
OL,14,Fa very serious inspection, we wanted
OL,15,Fto make sure officially there is
OL,16,Fnothing inside, no weapons here,
OL,17,Fnobody is hiding here, and we didn't
OL,18,Fwant any excuse for any bombing of
OL,19,Fthis temple."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780707788
OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FThe temple is under very strict
OL,8,Fsupervision by the Lebanese police to
OL,9,Fmake sure no one and nothing is hiding
OL,10,Fthere, to make it clear and say it out
OL,11,Floud, 'there is no reason to attack
OL,12,Fhere.'
OL,14,FLebanon's Culture Minister, Ghassan
OL,15,FSalame told us the difference between
OL,16,Fthe way the Germans and the Allies
OL,17,Fprotected Italy's Culture during WWII
OL,18,Fis stark.
OL,26,@wD@Frr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780707788
OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FHe said: "The Germans as well as the
OL,8,FAllies thought clearly in the depths
OL,9,Fof their hearts that Italian
OL,10,Fartefacts, buildings, and heritage are
OL,11,Fpart of their own heritage, but I
OL,12,Fdon't think the Israeli army had the
OL,13,Fsame feeling."
OL,15,FBeaufort Castle, a 900-year-old
OL,16,FCrusader fortress, is currently
OL,17,Foccupied by the IDF. Yesterday, an
OL,18,Fairstrike was carried out within its
OL,19,Fgrounds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
