PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780707788
OL,3,CHeritage sites in Lebanon hit by
OL,4,CIsraeli airstrikes despite UNESCO
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FOver 3,500 people have been killed in
OL,8,FLebanon since the latest war between
OL,9,FIsrael and Hezbollah began. Amid the
OL,10,Ftragic human losses in this war, the
OL,11,Fworld is also losing some of its most
OL,12,Fprecious cultural history.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
